channel.title: My personal IP - Deception Server Online Help
channel.description: So I used my IP last time, and successfully got this server online, but when I turn my computer off, then I go on. The server won't work. Last night I had like 3 people on it, it worked fine. It wont load now. I portfowarded and everything. I am using my ip from whatsmyip.org. I portfowarded to this computer to keep online but still doesnt work. Someone please help, I am using this server http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,474816.0.html

item.dc:creator: @Aceron4 Aceron4
item.description:
@Aceron4 wrote:

Alright so. Go to your network settings. Open up the the connection you are on. You should see a button with “Details” on it. (BTW Im on windows 7 … not sure what operating system your using) But anyway after you click that you should see all kinds of information about the connection. Locate the IPv4 address and use that when you go to portfoward.
